Title: 123: How to be Unstoppable: Data Science, Reckless Commitment & Artificial Intelligence
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the unstoppable, Rico Meinl. You will learn the practical applications of AI and why it is important, know the different tactics for applying your passion while still learning, and listen to a discussion on how to set up an AI lab at an e-commerce-ready company.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/123
